Re:          Unauthorized Use of Intellectual Property  
 
  
 
Dear Designated Agent: 
 
  
 
We have been retained by our Sony Television, Net Enforcers, Inc., to contact you
with respect to unauthorized use of Sony's trademarks and/or copyrighted materials. 
 
 
  
 
SONY TELEVISION has retained Net Enforcers to assist with the protection and
enforcement of its rights in SONY TELEVISION-owned or licensed trademarks, logos,
and other copyrighted materials.  Net Enforcers has in turn retained us to assist
with this matter.  Pursuant to 17 U.S.C. § 512 (c)(3)(A) and 15 U.S.C. § 1125(a)
and 1114 et seq, we hereby notify you of SONY TELEVISION's good faith belief that
your Client, Joe Saideh, at the URL www.infinitiphoto.com, is using SONY TELEVISION
trademarks and/or copyrighted materials without authorization by SONY TELEVISION,
its agents, or the law, specifically with respect to Sony Television products sold
by SONY TELEVISION's Division.  SONY TELEVISION has a good faith belief that the
information contained in this letter is accurate, and under penalty of perjury, Net
Enforcers is authorized to act on behalf of SONY TELEVISION. 
 
  
 
            The specific works, graphics or other material SONY TELEVISION believes
to be infringed or to be the subject of infringing activity (the
"Infringing Material") are copyrighted images from SONY TELEVISION's
website.  Specific violations of copyrighted images by infinitiphoto.com
are listed below this paragraph. 
 
  
 
http://www.infinitiphoto.com/viewitem-7360--Sony-Bravia-XBR-KDL-V32XBR1-32-in.-HDTV-LCD-Television

 
http://www.infinitiphoto.com/viewitem-8107--Sony-KDL-40S2000-40-IN-BRAVIA-S-Series-LCD-HDTV

 
  
 
            Therefore, pursuant to the requirements of 17 U.S.C. § 512(c)(1)(C),
SONY TELEVISION hereby demands that you remove or disable access to the
Infringing Material in an expeditious manner.   
 
  
 
  
 
If you have questions, please contact Net Enforcers Compliance Management Department
via facsimile to 352-505-0040, or via email to
Compliance.Management@NetEnforcers.com.  All communications should be in writing. 
SONY TELEVISION has authorized Net Enforcers to handle and resolve this matter with
you.  Please do not contact SONY TELEVISION directly, as SONY TELEVISION will simply
refer the matter back to Net Enforcers.  If your designated agent or representation
does not respond to this demand as requested by 5:00 p.m. on 10/3/2006, we will
assume that this demand has been rejected and proceed accordingly. 
 
Sincerely, 
 
VCLM Law 
 
  
 
Lance C. Venable 
 
Attorney at Law 
 
  
 
LCV/roc 
 
  
 
  
 
  
 
 
 
 
  
 
 
